OL,3,CEverything you need to know ahead
OL,4,CSevern bridge and tunnel closures
OL,6,FTravellers on the busiest routes
OL,7,Fbetween south Wales and England will
OL,8,Fface disruption in July as both the M4
OL,9,FSevern Bridge and Severn rail tunnel
OL,10,Fwill close for repairs on various
OL,11,Fdates between Wednesday 3 July and
OL,12,FFriday 19 July.
OL,14,FWhile GWR services will operate as
OL,15,Fusual between Pembroke Dock and
OL,16,FNewport, all services via the Severn
OL,17,FTunnel will be affected.
