OL,3,CEverything you need to know ahead
OL,4,CSevern bridge and tunnel closures
OL,6,FTrains from south Wales to London will
OL,7,Fbe rerouted via Gloucester. Limited
OL,8,Freplacement buses will be available
OL,9,Fbetween Bristol Parkway and Newport
OL,10,Fbut only on Sundays.
OL,12,FWhen are the closures?
OL,14,FThe disruption is scheduled from
OL,15,FWednesday 3 July to Thursday 18 July,
OL,16,Fand then again on the weekend of July
OL,17,F27 and 28.
