OL,3,CEverything you need to know ahead
OL,4,CSevern bridge and tunnel closures
OL,6,FHighways England, which maintains the
OL,7,Ftwo Severn bridges, warned commuters
OL,8,Fthey will face delays until autumn as
OL,9,Fthere will be a two-lane contraflow on
OL,10,Fthe bridge so workers can do
OL,11,Fresurfacing work.
OL,13,FIt means that on these days, the only
OL,14,Fmain route between south Wales and the
OL,15,Fsouth west of England will be over the
OL,16,FM48 bridge linking Chepstow and Aust.
OL,18,FWhy are the Severn bridge and tunnel
OL,19,Fshutting?
