OL,3,CEverything you need to know ahead
OL,4,CSevern bridge and tunnel closures
OL,6,FHighways England said that because the
OL,7,Froad surface on the M48 Severn Bridge
OL,8,Fis much narrower than a typical
OL,9,Fmotorway, there is less space for
OL,10,Fmaintenance to be carries out -
OL,11,Fresulting in them having to close the
OL,12,FSevern Bridge more often than most
OL,13,Fother motorways.
OL,15,FThe closures will allow workers to
OL,16,F"keep them in a safe and serviceable
OL,17,Fcondition."
