OL,3,CEverything you need to know ahead
OL,4,CSevern bridge and tunnel closures
OL,6,FNetwork Rail said they'll be
OL,7,F"replacing track over 4 miles of track
OL,8,Fin the Severn Tunnel to keep train
OL,9,Fservices safe and reliable along this
OL,10,Fbusy route."
OL,12,FThe team will also install 10,800
OL,13,Fsleepers and more than 22,000 tonnes
OL,14,Fof new ballast and remove 21,000
OL,15,Ftonnes of spoil.
OL,17,FIt will be closed for 16 days between
OL,18,FWednesday 3 July until the early hours
OL,19,Fof Friday 19 July, when train services
OL,20,Fare due to resume.
